<br>
You make it sound like a TV Movie, as if the people just use the insanity plea as a get out of jail free card. If the person is in fact innocent by reason of insanity, they will NEED to go to a mental institution until they are deemed legitimate for society. If they are found guilty by reason of insanity, I believe they go to a mental institution, and then go to jail. <br>
<br>
<br>
When they are found innocent, they are given help! Why destroy life when we can save it? The family of the killed wants revenge! What kind of blood thirsty society do we live in?! When the person is (if ever) finally cured of their mental disease, they are a new person! The person who committed the awful crimes is gone.<br>
<br>
As I said before, Why Destroy life when we can save it? Or fix it?<br>
